sect1:
Installing M4-&m4-version;



The M4 package contains a macro processor.

&buildtime; &m4-time;
&diskspace; &m4-compsize;

&aa-m4-down;
&aa-m4-dep;

 
 


Installation of M4


Prepare M4 for compilation:

./configure --prefix=/usr


Compile the package:

make


To have the results tested, issue:
make check.


And install the package:

make install



